16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 17-107B of Title 11, unless
19 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 There is hereby re-created in the State Treasury a revolving
21 fund for the State Auditor and Inspector to be designated the
22 "Special Investigative Unit Auditing Revolving Fund". The fund
23 shall be a continuing fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations,
24 and shall consist of all monies received by the State Auditor and
